sources.title: The Traveler (Mr. Nobody) | Full Movie | Action Thriller | Val Kilmer
sources.description:
The Traveler (Mr. Nobody) - A creepy drifter, calling himself Mr. Nobody (Val Kilmer), enters the Slaton, New York police station on Christmas Eve. He immediately confesses to having murdered six people. When people in the office start dying exactly like Mr. Nobody’s confessions, the officers must face their own dark past and this seemingly supernatural force.
2010.  Stars: Val Kilmer, Dylan Neal, Paul McGillion

metadata.Plot: A bloody, and gruesome thriller, THE TRAVELER stars Val Kilmer as a mysterious stranger whose past threatens to haunt the lives of six unsuspecting sheriff's deputies. The moment he arrives in their small town police station confessing to multiple murders, their lives are forever changed.forever...
